This is an experiment in providing the best way to embed the ODE BPEL engine for use
in other environments, e.g. SCA and more specifically the JBoss Switchyard project.




NOTES
=====

The following is the list of jars used in the original embedded test, and may provide
an indication of the minimum set of dependencies required. The maven project does not
restrict the extended list of dependencies pulled in currently.

